<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.5.9">
<l>vāṉattum vāṉattuḷ ḷumparu maṇṇuḷḷu maṇṇiṉkīḻt</l>
<l>tāṉattu meṇṭicai yuntavi rātuniṉ ṟāṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>kūṉaṟcaṅ kattaṭak kaiyavaṉaik kuṭamāṭiyai vāṉak</l>
<l>kōṉaik, kavicolla vallēṟ kiṉimā ṟuṇṭō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who stands without interruption in heaven, beyond the inside of heaven,</l>
<l>on earth, in the place below earth, and in the eight directions,</l>
<l>he with the curved conch in [his] broad hand, he who danced on a pot, the celestial</l>
<l>king, to me who is able to speak a poem on him, will there be opposition now?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
